        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Are you already treating folded lines differently from non-folded lines? If so I suggest using `virt_text_win_col` instead of `overlay`.\r\n\r\nEven in v0.9.0 `virt_text_win_col` is more reliable than `overlay` on folded lines:\r\n- `overlay` behaves confusingly on folded lines if the column of the extmark is not 0: only shown if the extmark is hidden by 'nowrap'.\r\n- `virt_text_win_col` always works, even if the column of the extmark is not 0.",
